19
00:00:17,272 --> 00:00:19,524
<i>Blinded by the dark side!</i>

20
00:00:19,608 --> 00:00:22,360
<i>The Jedi Council
has begun to unravel the mystery</i>

21
00:00:22,444 --> 00:00:24,946
<i>of how the clone army was created.</i>

22
00:00:25,030 --> 00:00:29,117
<i>And now fear the Sith Lord,
Count Dooku was behind it.</i>

23
00:00:29,201 --> 00:00:31,369
<i>Master Yoda searches for answers.</i>

24
00:00:31,453 --> 00:00:33,205
<i>And during deep meditation,</i>

25
00:00:33,288 --> 00:00:36,666
<i>he is able to contact
the spirit of Qui-Gon Jinn,</i>

26
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:40,962
<i>who reveals to Yoda that he must
manifest his consciousness after death</i>

27
00:00:41,046 --> 00:00:44,007
<i>if he is to preserve the Jedi Order.</i>

28
00:00:44,090 --> 00:00:47,052
<i>Now, we find Master Yoda
deep in space</i>

29
00:00:47,135 --> 00:00:49,846
<i>searching for a path to
ones who will teach him</i>

30
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:53,058
<i>all he does not know of the Force.</i>

31
00:00:58,355 --> 00:01:01,858
The place Qui-Gon spoke of
I believe this is.

32
00:01:07,697 --> 00:01:10,075
So, blocking our scanners the gas is.

33
00:01:10,325 --> 00:01:13,161
But inside a planet may be.

34
00:01:14,162 --> 00:01:15,664
Sense it I do.

35
00:01:36,977 --> 00:01:38,270
Controlling this are you?

36
00:01:44,192 --> 00:01:46,903
Let the Force guide I will.

37
00:02:37,704 --> 00:02:40,623
Awake again you are, my little friend.

38
00:02:41,333 --> 00:02:43,793
Where we are I'm not sure.

39
00:02:43,877 --> 00:02:46,713
But strong with the Force this place is.

40
00:02:55,513 --> 00:02:57,265
There you see?

41
00:02:57,349 --> 00:03:00,727
From inside the planet life emanates.

42
00:03:05,690 --> 00:03:08,651
Here, nothing your scanners can see?

43
00:03:09,903 --> 00:03:12,155
Need this, I will not.

44
00:03:15,784 --> 00:03:21,623
No, wait here you must.
A journey for me alone this is.

45
00:03:24,876 --> 00:03:27,128
Safer here you are, my friend.

46
00:04:25,937 --> 00:04:27,480
<i>Yoda.</i>

47
00:04:28,148 --> 00:04:29,649
Who is there?

48
00:04:29,732 --> 00:04:30,775
<i>Yoda.</i>

49
00:04:34,529 --> 00:04:38,783
Travel led far I have,
looking for those who can teach me.

50
00:04:39,367 --> 00:04:44,164
The question is,
are you worthy of being taught?

51
00:04:54,507 --> 00:04:55,842
You are late.

52
00:04:55,925 --> 00:04:58,595
We have been
waiting for you, Master Yoda.

53
00:04:58,887 --> 00:05:02,098
Late? How did you know coming I was?

54
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:07,479
We watch and study all who are
strong with the Force in the universe.

55
00:05:07,562 --> 00:05:10,356
Now come, if we are to begin.

56
00:05:44,057 --> 00:05:46,601
Cousins, I have a guest.

57
00:05:49,604 --> 00:05:53,066
You should not have
brought him before us?

58
00:05:53,316 --> 00:05:57,570
Nonsense, he is full of the Force.
Can you not feel it?

59
00:05:57,654 --> 00:05:59,989
Why is he here?

60
00:06:00,657 --> 00:06:03,326
Why are you here?

61
00:06:04,536 --> 00:06:07,121
Told I was to learn to from you.

62
00:06:07,205 --> 00:06:11,751
That show me you could
how to manifest my life after death.

63
00:06:12,168 --> 00:06:16,548
That's impossible!
He will fail the great gift.

64
00:06:16,631 --> 00:06:19,968
He will disappoint us.
He will disappoint himself.

65
00:06:20,635 --> 00:06:24,138
No. No, I do not see that.

66
00:06:24,222 --> 00:06:29,185
His destiny is already set.
It is not for us to decide.

67
00:06:29,644 --> 00:06:31,896
But why him?

68
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:36,693
He is to teach one that will save
the universe from a great imbalance.

69
00:06:36,776 --> 00:06:40,572
For this, the great gift will be his.

70
00:06:41,739 --> 00:06:46,202
He has no idea what he seeks!
The responsibility he will have!

71
00:06:46,828 --> 00:06:49,038
Understand I do not.

72
00:06:49,747 --> 00:06:51,332
Guide me I know you will.

73
00:06:51,416 --> 00:06:55,670
And do you realize what you must do?
What you must face?

74
00:06:57,005 --> 00:06:58,047
No.

75
00:06:58,423 --> 00:07:01,384
Good. Then you won't be afraid.

76
00:07:08,224 --> 00:07:12,061
Do I have our blessing
that the training can begin?

77
00:07:13,938 --> 00:07:18,443
It is so.
We are one and one is all.

78
00:07:19,611 --> 00:07:23,948
Do you come to us with only
good intention and light in your heart?

79
00:07:24,824 --> 00:07:26,534
I do. Yes.

80
00:07:27,535 --> 00:07:32,290
Then the blessing I give,
and the training will begin.

81
00:07:41,424 --> 00:07:44,636
Disappoint us not, little green one.

82
00:07:53,728 --> 00:07:55,355
What is this place?

83
00:07:55,438 --> 00:07:59,025
All that surrounds us
is the foundation of life.

84
00:07:59,108 --> 00:08:03,321
The birthplace of what your science
calls "midi-chlorians."

85
00:08:03,404 --> 00:08:08,409
The foundation of what connects
the living Force and the cosmic Force.

86
00:08:08,910 --> 00:08:12,705
When a living thing dies, all is renewed.

87
00:08:12,789 --> 00:08:16,668
Life passes from the living Force
into the cosmic Force

88
00:08:17,418 --> 00:08:19,587
and becomes one with it.

89
00:08:19,671 --> 00:08:22,423
One powers the other.

90
00:08:22,507 --> 00:08:25,468
One is renewed by the other.

91
00:08:26,427 --> 00:08:27,679
This I know.

92
00:08:28,805 --> 00:08:30,640
Come with me.

93
00:08:36,229 --> 00:08:40,108
At death, in order for you to preserve
your identity,

94
00:08:40,316 --> 00:08:46,280
you must know yourself, your true self,
and then let go.

95
00:08:47,073 --> 00:08:51,536
On that island dwells
all that remains unconquered,

96
00:08:51,619 --> 00:08:54,330
what in your existence some call evil,

97
00:08:54,872 --> 00:08:57,291
otherwise known as fear.

98
00:08:57,667 --> 00:09:03,089
All which must be finally overcome
before the journey can be taken.

99
00:09:03,548 --> 00:09:06,259
Free yourself you must.

100
00:09:06,551 --> 00:09:08,886
A Jedi Master I am.

101
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:11,639
Know all that dwells within I do.

102
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:15,727
Mastered my weaknesses
and conquered my fears I have.

103
00:09:16,102 --> 00:09:17,812
Have you?

104
00:09:17,895 --> 00:09:22,567
You must face your evil on that island
and defeat it.

105
00:09:54,432 --> 00:09:56,809
Yoda.

106
00:10:08,404 --> 00:10:10,698
Yoda.

107
00:10:23,127 --> 00:10:25,922
Yoda.

108
00:10:27,048 --> 00:10:28,674
Show yourself.

109
00:10:31,886 --> 00:10:35,598
Yoda hates me, yes?

110
00:10:43,022 --> 00:10:46,526
Yoda plays not with me anymore!

111
00:10:46,609 --> 00:10:49,737
Yoda thinks me not worthy.

112
00:11:02,708 --> 00:11:04,669
Yoda recognizes you not!

113
00:11:06,212 --> 00:11:09,674
See not what is inside Yoda?

114
00:11:09,757 --> 00:11:12,009
I choose not to give you power.

115
00:11:12,093 --> 00:11:16,347
And yet you spend your days
in the decadence of war.

116
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:19,934
And with that, I grow inside you.

117
00:11:20,017 --> 00:11:22,520
Know your true self.

118
00:11:22,603 --> 00:11:26,983
Face me now, or I will devour you.

119
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,340
Part of me you are not!

120
00:11:52,383 --> 00:11:56,721
Part of you I am.
Part of all that lives.

121
00:12:03,311 --> 00:12:06,480
Why do you hate
what gives you power?

122
00:12:18,993 --> 00:12:22,496
Yoda thinks me not worthy.

123
00:12:25,583 --> 00:12:28,002
Recognize you I do.

124
00:12:38,387 --> 00:12:40,681
Part of me you are, yes.

125
00:12:44,602 --> 00:12:47,104
But power over me you have not.

126
00:12:47,188 --> 00:12:50,524
Through patience and training,
it is I who control you.

127
00:12:55,029 --> 00:12:58,199
Control over me you have not.

128
00:13:02,286 --> 00:13:05,623
My dark side you are.
Reject you I do.

129
00:13:20,054 --> 00:13:22,640
You have conquered your hubris.

130
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:27,979
Now face the temptations you must.

131
00:13:37,238 --> 00:13:39,949
Powerful the creature was.

132
00:13:40,741 --> 00:13:43,327
What you faced was a reflection of

133
00:13:43,411 --> 00:13:45,705
your hubris and
the shadow of your soul.

134
00:13:46,414 --> 00:13:49,250
And yet, clear I thought I was.

135
00:13:49,917 --> 00:13:54,547
The beast is you
and you are the beast.

136
00:13:55,381 --> 00:13:58,217
To deny it simply gives it power.

137
00:13:58,300 --> 00:14:01,178
Now I see.
Simple the answer was.

138
00:14:03,597 --> 00:14:08,102
Deep in your core you felt that
we had nothing to teach you.

139
00:14:08,185 --> 00:14:12,565
But you must trust in our teachings
if you are to succeed.

140
00:14:14,191 --> 00:14:17,111
Ready I am for what comes next.

141
00:14:18,446 --> 00:14:22,283
You must enter the valley of extinction.

142
00:14:25,828 --> 00:14:30,916
Pass through without emotion,
without attachment.

143
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:36,255
For you will see all our faces there
and they will seduce you.

144
00:14:36,547 --> 00:14:38,883
For we are Confusion.

145
00:14:39,383 --> 00:14:40,885
Anger.

146
00:14:40,968 --> 00:14:42,470
Sadness.

147
00:14:42,553 --> 00:14:44,055
Joy.

148
00:14:44,138 --> 00:14:46,932
And Serenity.

149
00:14:59,070 --> 00:15:01,238
Stop! Stop!

150
00:15:03,115 --> 00:15:05,743
No! No! No!

151
00:15:30,768 --> 00:15:36,440
Master Yoda.
Please, help me.

152
00:15:38,359 --> 00:15:40,194
I'm dying.

153
00:15:40,277 --> 00:15:43,239
What has happened here, Padawan?

154
00:15:43,322 --> 00:15:44,990
Who has done this?

155
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,538
The Sith.

156
00:15:51,122 --> 00:15:52,373
How?

157
00:15:52,456 --> 00:15:56,794
You told me I would finish my training
and become a Jedi,

158
00:15:56,877 --> 00:15:59,255
but the council expelled me.

159
00:15:59,338 --> 00:16:01,590
Why would you do that?

160
00:16:03,217 --> 00:16:08,139
Will I still become one with the Force
when I die?

161
00:16:08,597 --> 00:16:12,810
Master, will I be a Jedi?

162
00:16:12,893 --> 00:16:16,063
Padawan?
Padawan. Ahsoka.

163
00:16:16,564 --> 00:16:19,525
No! No! No!

164
00:16:20,151 --> 00:16:23,320
Not strong enough I was. No!

165
00:16:23,988 --> 00:16:27,324
Failed I have.
Failed them all.

166
00:16:28,826 --> 00:16:30,703
Master Yoda.

167
00:16:31,996 --> 00:16:34,623
Let me take you away
from your confusion,

168
00:16:34,707 --> 00:16:38,210
your anger, your sadness!

169
00:16:40,254 --> 00:16:43,841
Come with me
and you will never know pain.

170
00:16:43,924 --> 00:16:45,676
Never know sadness.

171
00:16:48,971 --> 00:16:52,933
Close your eyes,
and I will guide you.

172
00:17:05,029 --> 00:17:09,533
The temple is beautiful,
isn't it, Master Yoda?

173
00:17:17,541 --> 00:17:22,630
Yes, so peaceful,
as it was before the war.

174
00:17:22,755 --> 00:17:26,550
War? There is no war here, Master.

175
00:17:26,634 --> 00:17:29,511
Only peace and tranquility.

176
00:17:30,638 --> 00:17:32,389
No war?

177
00:17:44,485 --> 00:17:45,945
Master Yoda.

178
00:17:46,028 --> 00:17:49,907
Master Dooku was just telling us
a tale of when he was your Padawan.

179
00:17:49,990 --> 00:17:52,159
Really quite a humorous story.

180
00:17:52,368 --> 00:17:53,869
Count Dooku!

181
00:17:54,495 --> 00:17:55,913
Yes, Master.

182
00:17:55,996 --> 00:18:01,293
I was telling them the tale of when you
faced the giant terentatek on Kashyyyk.

183
00:18:01,377 --> 00:18:03,170
What a terrible beast it was.

184
00:18:04,505 --> 00:18:07,299
Yes, yes.

185
00:18:07,383 --> 00:18:09,176
I remember.

186
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:13,055
We had wonderful adventures,
Master Yoda and I.

187
00:18:13,138 --> 00:18:16,642
I'm sure we'd all love to hear more,
but it's time to join the others.

188
00:18:20,854 --> 00:18:22,648
Coming, Master?

189
00:18:34,618 --> 00:18:37,496
No, wrong this is.

190
00:18:38,330 --> 00:18:39,790
Lies, these images are!

191
00:18:39,873 --> 00:18:41,458
Lies!

192
00:18:43,794 --> 00:18:44,878
Dead, I know you to be!

193
00:18:46,547 --> 00:18:49,216
On Naboo, died you did, Qui-Gon.

194
00:18:51,218 --> 00:18:54,179
And a traitor you are,
my old Padawan.

195
00:19:10,779 --> 00:19:14,241
No! An illusion this is!
A falsehood!

196
00:19:32,217 --> 00:19:33,761
You have done well.

197
00:19:34,261 --> 00:19:35,387
But to succeed,

198
00:19:35,471 --> 00:19:39,683
your life must be
spent learning, practicing.

199
00:19:40,768 --> 00:19:43,937
Please. Show me who you are.

200
00:19:44,021 --> 00:19:46,440
See your face I must.

201
00:19:55,074 --> 00:19:57,117
<i>Now you see.</i>

202
00:19:57,201 --> 00:20:02,206
<i>We have achieved what you seek,
and live between the realms.</i>

203
00:20:02,289 --> 00:20:04,124
Dead you are?

204
00:20:04,875 --> 00:20:06,460
<i>Yes.</i>

205
00:20:07,127 --> 00:20:09,546
How shall I complete my training?

206
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:14,551
You must face the ultimate test.

207
00:20:14,635 --> 00:20:16,470
The ultimate seduction.

208
00:20:16,553 --> 00:20:18,764
The gravest of journeys.

209
00:20:19,556 --> 00:20:21,975
You will travel to Moraband...

210
00:20:22,184 --> 00:20:23,352
Moraband?

211
00:20:23,685 --> 00:20:26,397
Journey through the ancient home world
of the Sith.

212
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,899
Face all that you fear.

213
00:20:28,982 --> 00:20:32,528
All that haunts your soul!

214
00:20:54,383 --> 00:20:56,135
Hello, my friend.

215
00:20:57,136 --> 00:21:01,014
No, no.
One more place to visit we have.

216
00:21:08,856 --> 00:21:13,777
A strange place I have come from,
but finished not what I came for.

217
00:21:14,653 --> 00:21:17,030
Set a course for Moraband.

218
00:21:19,825 --> 00:21:22,619
Yes, brave we must be.

219
00:21:23,162 --> 00:21:26,290
The worst, I fear, is yet to come.

220
00:21:26,314 --> 00:21:31,314
http://hiqve.com/

